Known affectionately as 'Wee Jay', the youngster accompanied Celtic for their 2-0 defeat of Hamilton on January 19 where he met players and was asked to take part in a shootout challenge during the interval - which he duly obliged and scored before celebrating wildly in front of Celtic fans.

Despite losing 2-0, Hamilton had the good grace to include Beatty's strike in their final score, announcing it as 3-0 to Celtic on Twitter.

